"personers rätt att använda eventuella ändringar som du gör i programmet, "
"etc. läs då licensen. Du hittar den i filen <filename>COPYING</filename> i "
"&kig;s källkod, eller med länken till licensen i dialogrutan <guilabel>Om "
"&kig;</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to contribute ?"
msgstr "Hur kan jag bidra?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any contributions are welcome. If you don't like the icons, or think that "
"the manual needs updating, or if you have this really cool macro that you "
"want to share with the world, do not hesitate to send it to me. Please note "
"that your contributions will be distributed under the terms of the &GNU; "
